Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.76,0:00:01.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Darkness and Light!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.92,0:00:03.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Into the chaos of\nthe Feudal Era,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.59,0:00:05.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Sacred Jewel brings a group\nof strangers together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.06,0:00:07.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}500 years across time,\ntheirdestinies are controlled{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.56,0:00:11.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}by the few remaining shards\nof the Jewel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.80,0:00:13.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Feudal Fairy Tale:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.30,0:00:14.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.17,0:00:18.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It all started fifty years ago.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.37,0:00:21.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My sister Kikyo and Inuyasha...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.68,0:00:23.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}a love song of their\ntragic destiny.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.71,0:02:06.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My name is Kaede.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.55,0:02:09.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am an old priestess\nwho has survived{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.68,0:02:11.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}through a violent age where\nwars nevercease.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.72,0:02:12.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.96,0:02:15.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.52,0:02:17.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But back then, I was just\nan innocent girl{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.69,0:02:21.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}who knew nothing of\nfighting orwar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:28.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.97,0:02:32.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.91,0:02:35.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do not come, Kaede!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.34,0:02:37.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:38.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:46.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That lady {\i1}is....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.13,0:02:54.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,a priestess named Tsubaki,\nisn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.87,0:02:58.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.93,0:03:01.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is thatgirl yourlittle sister, Kikyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.27,0:03:06.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you sure about this, Kikyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.21,0:03:09.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am perfectly capable\nof handling this alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:12.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take your sister and get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.55,0:03:14.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You need not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.92,0:03:17.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.45,0:03:19.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your own sistermay be\nin danger,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.35,0:03:21.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,yet you refuse to budge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:25.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:39.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A- Amazing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.54,0:03:43.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are such a cold woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.81,0:03:45.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, you are not a {\i1}woman....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.88,0:03:47.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you are definitely a priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.78,0:03:50.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, I am a priestess.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.22,0:03:52.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That is my destiny.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.83,0:04:02.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A strong, proud, beautiful priestess.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.60,0:04:06.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}In my youthful eyes, my sister\NKikyo was everything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:14.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I had no idea of the sad fate\nwhich awaited my sister.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.58,0:04:19.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Blast you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:22.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is not {\i1}over....{\i0}\nnot by a long shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:33.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:37.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where did you go, half-demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.53,0:04:38.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.47,0:04:42.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-Reaver, Soul-Stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.21,0:04:49.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.21,0:04:53.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No one calls me a "half-demon"\nand lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.73,0:05:14.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.17,0:05:16.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.07,0:05:18.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's the limestone cave!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:19.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please come!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.64,0:05:21.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's something wrong\nat the limestone cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.51,0:05:22.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.65,0:05:29.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.42,0:05:33.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you know what's happening, Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.32,0:05:33.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.79,0:05:36.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:38.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Chief! What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:40.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:42.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This must be Midoriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.46,0:05:47.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Midoriko? The legendary\npriestess who made the Sacred Jewel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.04,0:05:51.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's impossible! She's been\ndead forhundreds of years!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.21,0:05:55.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is this corpse?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.88,0:05:58.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's the demon we\nexterminated the day before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:06:00.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think it called itself\NMistress Centipede.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.05,0:06:02.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It gave us a lot of trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:04.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but we smashed its head,\nso it should be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.79,0:06:11.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:12.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.70,0:06:18.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:19.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:22.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Midoriko's soul is reacting\nto this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:26.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Chief, could that {\i1}be....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:28.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm seeing it for\nthe first time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:30.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.48,0:06:35.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Kirara?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.55,0:06:37.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:39.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Everyone, get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.05,0:06:42.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That belongs to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:46.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:48.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give back the Sacred Jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.33,0:06:51.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.87,0:07:00.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:07.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:09.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.58,0:07:11.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Chief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:15.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's the power of the Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:18.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As long as this jewel is nearby,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:22.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,it will... keep on reviving.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.40,0:07:29.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't let itget away, Kirara!\NGo afterit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:38.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! We can't do anything\nabout this tainted jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.15,0:07:39.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We must find a priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.68,0:07:41.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:45.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Find a priestess with the power\nto purify this Sacred {\i1}Jewel....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:51.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My sister Kikyo and I wandered\nthe countryside training and{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.73,0:07:54.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}exterminating demons.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:57.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you sure you don't want\nyourreward?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.73,0:08:00.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes. You may have it, Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.07,0:08:02.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see. Well then, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:08.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo, here is a bit of advice\nfrom one priestess to another.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.11,0:08:11.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When a priestess abandons all\nhuman feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.35,0:08:13.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,hertrue power comes alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.58,0:08:16.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But if one is a woman,\nit's only natural to fall in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:18.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Love?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:20.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Me, fall in love?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:23.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do not forget this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.36,0:08:24.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You must not fall in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.33,0:08:27.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do not let a man desire you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:30.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If such a man ever appears\nbefore you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:33.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you will die a violent death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:35.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Humph....{\i0} I shall remember\nthose words.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.18,0:08:47.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That Tsubaki is unscrupulous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.78,0:08:48.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.12,0:08:51.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She just placed a curse\non me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.12,0:08:52.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.12,0:08:55.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:59.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forthere is no way that\NI would fall in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:05.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You won't get away, half-demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:08.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll avenge our olderbrother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.37,0:09:11.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn! I didn't know he had\ntwo brothers!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.77,0:09:13.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.08,0:09:18.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.61,0:09:19.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well then, take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.18,0:09:21.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Blades of Blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.35,0:09:28.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...! Half-demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.52,0:09:32.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You got a problem with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.39,0:09:33.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:35.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-Reaver, Soul-Stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:44.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! To let these weaklings\nhurt {\i1}me....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.84,0:09:47.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must become stronger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:50.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must become much,\nmuch stronger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:10:00.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Mistress Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:05.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mistress {\i1}Kikyo....{\i0} Ademon slayer\ncame looking for you this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:08.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When I explained that\nyou were away,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.26,0:10:10.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,he said he'd return tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.83,0:10:11.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ademon slayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.37,0:10:13.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder what he wants?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.77,0:10:19.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister! Hurry and\ncome inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:36.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister! What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.96,0:10:39.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.29,0:10:41.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It is known as the Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.33,0:10:45.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have been given the duty\nof purifying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:50.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was the first time I laid\neyes on the Sacred Jewel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.31,0:10:54.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And after she took\ncustody of the Jewel,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.51,0:10:57.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}my sister Kikyo's destiny\nchanged drastically.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.81,0:11:01.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Othergirls herage\nwere burning perfume incense,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.98,0:11:04.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}coloring theirlips\nand cheeks...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:07.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and enjoying theiryouthfulness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.39,0:11:14.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must hurry tonight!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.43,0:11:17.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.83,0:11:20.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn, it stinks of blood!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.25,0:11:39.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A mortal woman?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.25,0:11:41.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that truly a woman?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.62,0:11:43.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.46,0:11:46.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's starting!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.37,0:11:53.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How long do you intend to hide?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:09.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you after the Sacred Jewel, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.82,0:12:13.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sacred Jewel? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.49,0:12:20.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you don't know it,\nthat's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.46,0:12:23.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However, if you do not want\nto be killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.43,0:12:25.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,never appear before me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.69,0:12:50.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What kind of priestess is {\i1}she....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:56.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mistress Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:13:00.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mistress Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.24,0:13:02.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:04.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.71,0:13:06.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mistress Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:08.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.71,0:13:09.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:12.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kaede....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:13.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.88,0:13:14.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:21.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm....{\i0} He let me live.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:24.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am not without luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.93,0:13:27.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's {\i1}near....{\i0} It's very near!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:29.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Sacred Jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.93,0:13:32.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I must increase my demon power,\nor my body will not last.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.34,0:13:38.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So that's what it's all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.51,0:13:40.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Sacred Jewel, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:42.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sounds interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:47.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And hername is {\i1}Kikyo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.09,0:13:56.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:14:00.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I hear the Sacred Jewel is\na sphere of good fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:02.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that increases the power\nof a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:03.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That {\i1}voice....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.43,0:14:05.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've heard it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.77,0:14:11.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see, you're the one who was\nhiding in the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:12.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.11,0:14:14.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give me that Sacred Jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:15.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whaa...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.61,0:14:22.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I understand now. I thought\NI sensed a different aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.15,0:14:24.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are a half-demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.32,0:14:28.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With the Sacred Jewel,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.82,0:14:31.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you can indeed become\na complete demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.73,0:14:35.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Would you go that farto\nfind your place in the world, half-demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:38.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you believe that\nis true power?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.70,0:14:41.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.34,0:14:43.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll become the strongest demon around!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.50,0:14:44.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's what I've decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:49.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And when I do, I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:50.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Humph!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:55.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As long as I am the one purifying\nand protecting it, that will not happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.85,0:14:56.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:15:00.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You reek with the smell\nof demon blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.66,0:15:05.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? Did I touch a nerve with that, Kikyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.89,0:15:08.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you don't want to be killed,\nstay away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:11.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Remember, there will be\nno third time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.77,0:15:14.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! I'm notgiving up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.40,0:15:16.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if you run away, I'll find you\nwithout fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.30,0:15:21.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With that smell, I'll find you quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:23.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Smell....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:39.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.06,0:15:42.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister {\i1}Kikyo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:45.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then, let us go home, Kaede.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.33,0:15:45.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:46.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.70,0:15:48.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.04,0:15:52.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Kikyo, give me\nthe Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.04,0:15:54.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you've appeared again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.51,0:15:58.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I told you that I wouldn't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.01,0:16:00.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And we're gonna settle this today!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:03.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry and tell that kid to run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.22,0:16:05.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kaede, get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.99,0:16:07.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister {\i1}Kikyo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.63,0:16:15.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Apriestess that walks a bloody bath.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.30,0:16:20.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}An existence that is neither human\nnordemon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:24.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Apitiful half-demon looking\nforhis place in this world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.41,0:16:29.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There is something I wish to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:33.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why didn't you kill me that night?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:37.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It would have been an easy task\nin my condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.32,0:16:40.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't pull dirty tricks like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:43.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.32,0:16:44.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:46.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let me ask you one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.46,0:16:49.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Half-demon, what are you called?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.10,0:16:53.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You do have a name, at least?\NEven if you're a half-demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:56.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Quit harping on the half-demon thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.90,0:16:58.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then tell {\i1}me....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.54,0:17:00.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I shall never call you\N"half-demon" again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.98,0:17:04.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.05,0:17:07.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha? I shall remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.32,0:17:10.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prepare to die, Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:22.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait up, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:25.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why do you always leave\nwithout killing me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.07,0:17:27.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop squirming around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.60,0:17:29.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My arrows are wasted on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:33.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was a mystery to me, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.37,0:17:38.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why didn't Sister Kikyo\nfinish Inuyasha off?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.21,0:17:41.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why didn't she use her\nsacred arrows on Inuyasha?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.92,0:17:44.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}From around that time,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.18,0:17:47.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo went to cleanse herself\nevery day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:54.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Looking back, I think it began\nfrom the day she met Inuyasha.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:17:59.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Saruhozuki....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.60,0:18:02.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I remember Kikyo telling me this\nhelps to reduce swelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.94,0:18:04.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Sacred Jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.91,0:18:11.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- I shall take you hostage...\N- Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:15.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and get the Sacred Jewel\nfrom Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.38,0:18:16.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get away, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:25.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! No way would I let a\nweakling demon like you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.96,0:18:28.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,have the Sacred Jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.86,0:18:29.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Um....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.66,0:18:30.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.30,0:18:33.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you for saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:35.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't get me wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:39.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,ljust don't want anyone else\nto have the Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:41.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was puzzled...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:48.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why didn't this Inuyasha take me\nhostage like Mistress Centipede?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:59.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sister Kikyo knew that the corpse\nof Mistress Centipede{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.56,0:19:02.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}still contained demon power.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.50,0:19:06.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The powerof the Sacred Jewel\ncannot reach in here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:12.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, you're there, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.81,0:19:13.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:20.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is the first time\nwe've spoken up close.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:21.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So what of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.48,0:19:24.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I understand you saved Kaede.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.75,0:19:26.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh {\i1}that....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.62,0:19:28.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want to thank you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.59,0:19:30.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't do something\nthat's unlike you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:37.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:40.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How do I look?\NDo I seem human?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:43.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.77,0:19:47.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I show my weakness to no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:49.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I must not hesitate,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.34,0:19:52.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so that demons cannot\novercome me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.85,0:19:57.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am human, yet I cannot\nbe human.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.99,0:20:00.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're alike, you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.19,0:20:02.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You, a {\i1}half-demon....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.32,0:20:05.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why I could not kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.86,0:20:09.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah? Making excuses?\NThat's not like you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.37,0:20:14.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess {\i1}so....{\i0} It's not like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:22.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.38,0:20:25.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:28.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, {\i1}nothing....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:33.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.16,0:20:38.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo! Come back here tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.73,0:20:40.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.56,0:20:41.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Err....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.50,0:20:44.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want to give you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.03,0:20:46.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You want to give me something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:50.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good, because I have something\NI've been thinking about giving you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:52.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? The Sacred Jewel?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:54.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.81,0:20:57.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I figured as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.22,0:21:09.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aren't those the Kotodama sutra beads?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.06,0:21:12.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you giving those to Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.56,0:21:14.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.80,0:21:16.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It may be underhanded of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.73,0:21:19.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but these will prevent him\nfrom doing any more wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.77,0:21:24.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now {\i1}then....{\i0} what trigger word\ncan I use to make the beads take effect?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.37,0:21:30.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}At that time, it seemed to me that\NKikyo looked sort of happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.81,0:21:37.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I remembernow....That priestess {\i1}Tsubaki....{\i0}\nput a strange curse on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.42,0:21:43.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh {\i1}well....{\i0} I walk the path of carnage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.49,0:21:46.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So why should I fear an\nunnatural death?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.79,0:21:48.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sister....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.23,0:21:53.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The triggerword will {\i1}be....{\i0}\N"beloved."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.81,0:22:00.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.44,0:22:05.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No sense in me keeping it.\NI'll give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.65,0:22:10.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The only things\nmy motherleft {\i1}me....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.75,0:22:13.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That and the Robe of the\NFire-rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.75,0:22:16.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yourmother was human?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.52,0:22:18.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah....well....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.49,0:22:20.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This must mean so much to {\i1}you....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.43,0:22:21.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.10,0:22:24.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Robe of the Fire-rat is\nuseful enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.47,0:22:31.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.64,0:22:34.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I didn't know and I shot so many\narrows at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.78,0:22:36.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.34,0:22:40.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,By the way, what were you gonna\ngive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:49.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.\NI must have {\i1}forgotten....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.66,0:22:52.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Geez! I was looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.13,0:22:54.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you sure I can have this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.63,0:22:58.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.84,0:23:10.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha and {\i1}Kikyo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.49,0:23:31.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That night, Kikyo colored\nherlips.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.33,0:23:34.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}She looked so beautiful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.10,0:23:37.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But even to my innocent eyes,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.94,0:23:40.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}there was a sadness\nabout her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.52,0:23:54.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now what would you like to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.09,0:24:02.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, come down from there\nand join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.50,0:24:04.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.76,0:24:05.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's play hand-ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.93,0:24:07.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's pick flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.31,0:24:22.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll neverbe as good as Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.12,0:24:27.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good for you, Kaede.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.79,0:24:29.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.73,0:24:33.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.06,0:24:38.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, {\i1}Sister....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.97,0:24:40.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.63,0:24:42.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.34,0:24:45.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.34,0:24:53.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to see Kikyo\nlook beautiful...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.21,0:24:55.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to help her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.12,0:25:00.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought I was the only one\nwith such thoughts.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.44,0:25:19.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}K-Kikyo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.77,0:25:22.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes. I brought some gruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.84,0:25:27.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't bother... with me {\i1}anymore....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.15,0:25:31.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.05,0:25:38.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo was harboring a bandit\nnamed Onigumo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.83,0:25:44.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why can't I tell Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.23,0:25:48.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Knowing him, he will probably\nbecome jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.87,0:25:50.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.81,0:25:56.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, lend me your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.48,0:25:58.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's this, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.45,0:26:00.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've been asked to exterminate\na demon from another country.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.35,0:26:04.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Buteven I will have\nmy hands full.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.45,0:26:07.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! This is gonna cost ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.06,0:26:13.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, it's coming yourway!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.66,0:26:14.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Leave 'im to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.36,0:26:17.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-Reaver, Soul-Stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.70,0:26:20.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo, that's its true form.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.87,0:26:21.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.91,0:26:27.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! You got 'im!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.08,0:26:36.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yo....kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.68,0:26:37.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's Kaede.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.02,0:26:42.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your sisterhas something\ncalled the Sacred Jewel, doesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.59,0:26:46.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How do you know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.96,0:26:50.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All bad guys are afterit.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.80,0:26:51.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.07,0:26:53.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And from what I {\i1}hear....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.67,0:26:56.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the Jewel becomes more evil when\nit absorbs blood filled with hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.50,0:26:58.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I like {\i1}that....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.01,0:27:00.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My sister is purifying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.71,0:27:02.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It will not become evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.24,0:27:05.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo always seems\nso serene.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.15,0:27:10.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How I'd love to see {\i1}her....{\i0}\nget all flustered.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.69,0:27:13.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I getexcited just\nthinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.03,0:27:21.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I {\i1}see....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.20,0:27:23.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So that's what Onigumo said.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.66,0:27:27.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister, I do not like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.50,0:27:28.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.17,0:27:34.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That man will probably nevermove\nfrom that spot for the rest of his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.44,0:27:37.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That is what SisterKikyo said.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.41,0:27:45.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I had a foreboding feeling\nabout her kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.72,0:27:50.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.32,0:27:54.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I understand if you stand\nbeneath the cherry trees for too long,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.73,0:27:56.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you will go insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.33,0:27:59.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's because\nof these cherry {\i1}trees....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.33,0:28:02.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you seem like a completely different\nperson from last I saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.84,0:28:06.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And your pitifully weak {\i1}powers....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.44,0:28:12.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Specters and demons are\nbreaking through yourbarrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.65,0:28:17.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I {\i1}see....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.42,0:28:20.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you were unleashing\nthe specters.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.02,0:28:23.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Letting yourheartgo\nto a {\i1}man....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.09,0:28:27.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And he is that worthless half-demon,\nis he not?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.90,0:28:32.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give me the Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.80,0:28:35.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I shall purify it\nin your stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.34,0:28:39.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Humph! You are not able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.94,0:28:43.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Die, Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.32,0:28:58.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn you, Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.96,0:29:03.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get back! I shall spare your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.68,0:29:17.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Onigumo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.61,0:29:20.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Onigumo....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.15,0:29:25.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your evil thoughts have\nbrought us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.42,0:29:28.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ademon?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.02,0:29:30.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will {\i1}listen....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.42,0:29:32.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.79,0:29:36.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want a body that will\nenable me to move freely,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.40,0:29:41.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so that I can make the Sacred Jewel\nand Kikyo mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.87,0:29:43.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Done.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.50,0:29:47.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But in return, we will take\nyour soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.48,0:29:53.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My rotten soul is worth\nsomething, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.55,0:29:56.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Doesn't it look tasty?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.62,0:29:58.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You want to eat me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.59,0:30:01.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go ahead....eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.49,0:30:05.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And give me a {\i1}body....{\i0}\nand power!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.88,0:30:25.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've improved greatly.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.41,0:30:26.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.91,0:30:28.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next is the Arrow of Sealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.02,0:30:30.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Arrow of Sealing?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.33,0:30:45.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is the sacred arrow,\NFuuin no Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.30,0:30:47.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We use it for demons\nwho are invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.50,0:30:50.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And then what happens\nto the demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.60,0:30:52.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They fall into an\neternal sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.31,0:30:56.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They will only awaken when\nthe one who shot the arrow
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.71,0:30:59.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,deeply wants the demon to revive.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.35,0:31:04.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However, Kaede, beware\nof this tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.42,0:31:06.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? The Sacred Tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.59,0:31:08.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is known as\nthe Tree of Ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.99,0:31:10.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It has the power to\ntranscend time.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.39,0:31:12.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tree of Ages?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.99,0:31:14.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you seal a demon\nto this tree,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.89,0:31:17.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the demon's body will\nremain {\i1}intact....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.83,0:31:18.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.50,0:31:22.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.34,0:31:24.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So many of {\i1}them....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.34,0:31:26.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ridiculous!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.24,0:31:28.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}How could I not notice\nan aura this strong?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.24,0:31:31.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go, specters!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.08,0:31:34.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go and take the Sacred Jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.52,0:31:39.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Sacred Jewel will give you\nimmense demon power!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.95,0:31:44.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Become the greatest demons of\nthem all and destroy the priestess, Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.84,0:31:57.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Specters!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.54,0:32:01.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-Reaver, Soul-Stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.91,0:32:06.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.78,0:32:08.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're late, Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.48,0:32:09.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.99,0:32:16.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My spiritual powers\nhave weakened.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.19,0:32:18.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right! Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.33,0:32:30.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Blades of Blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.84,0:32:31.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.01,0:32:33.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Watch out! Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.14,0:32:36.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kaede!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.95,0:32:40.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.25,0:32:42.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Kaede!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.12,0:32:48.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.84,0:33:13.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What happened to hereyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.65,0:33:16.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've done a terrible thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.55,0:33:19.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.85,0:33:22.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was too timid.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.39,0:33:26.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't blame yourself too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.83,0:33:29.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,These things happen all the time\nwhen you're fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.33,0:33:31.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.96,0:33:35.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you unable to be yourself\nunless you are fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.24,0:33:39.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You asked me something\nlike that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.97,0:33:42.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you like to\nstop fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.58,0:33:44.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.55,0:33:49.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop fighting and\nbecome human.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.35,0:33:50.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Me? A human?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.22,0:33:52.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can become one.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.62,0:33:55.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,After all, you are\nhalf human.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.66,0:34:01.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When the Sacred Jewel is\nin the hands of an evil demon,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.49,0:34:03.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,its evil powers increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.36,0:34:07.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But if I use it to\nmake you human,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.00,0:34:11.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,it will become purified\nand most likely, disintegrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.67,0:34:16.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But then, Kikyo, what will\nhappen to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.31,0:34:19.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am the protector\nof this Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.75,0:34:21.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And if the Jewel ceases\nto exist,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.18,0:34:22.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will become an ordinary woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.32,0:34:28.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.44,0:34:47.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.84,0:34:53.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo, I will become a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.35,0:34:56.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not saying this on a whim.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.42,0:34:58.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will become a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.59,0:35:00.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.56,0:35:04.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you can become\nan ordinary human, {\i1}too....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.79,0:35:06.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.86,0:35:07.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Enough....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.40,0:35:11.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do not say anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.43,0:35:12.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.00,0:35:14.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I {\i1}feel....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.51,0:35:26.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, are you\nsure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.58,0:35:28.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.22,0:35:30.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,About {\i1}me....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.98,0:35:32.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.52,0:35:35.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Do you even\nhave to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.42,0:35:37.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tomorrow {\i1}afternoon....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.66,0:35:38.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.03,0:35:41.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In front of the Sacred Tree\nin the western forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.69,0:35:42.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait forme there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.80,0:35:45.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will bring the\NSacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.57,0:35:48.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.77,0:35:53.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As if I {\i1}will....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.14,0:35:58.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,let her!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.19,0:36:16.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.43,0:36:17.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.36,0:36:20.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter?\NHas something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.97,0:36:22.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't wait any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.30,0:36:27.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo, can you make me\nhuman right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.77,0:36:29.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.38,0:36:31.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The night is filled with evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.31,0:36:35.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we are to use the Sacred Jewel,\nit must be afterthe sun rises.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.92,0:36:36.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.58,0:36:40.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then do it right after\nthe day breaks, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.12,0:36:43.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.89,0:36:46.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.43,0:36:54.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.98,0:37:07.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.48,0:37:10.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh....{\i0} Just out.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.32,0:37:16.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's still early.\NGo back to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.82,0:37:17.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.82,0:37:22.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm justgoing out to find\nmedicinal herbs foryour wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.56,0:37:24.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Medicinal herbs?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.16,0:37:27.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's a lot here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.67,0:37:28.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.30,0:37:32.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There may be something\nmore effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.01,0:37:34.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm going to take\nanotherlook.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.61,0:37:38.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.01,0:37:41.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kaede, do youreyes hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.32,0:37:44.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, it's much bettertoday.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.38,0:37:46.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.72,0:37:47.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll return right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.59,0:37:56.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}At that moment, I felt lonelierthan I'd\neverfelt before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.03,0:37:59.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted my sisterto\nstay with me forever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.03,0:38:02.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't want herto go\nanywhere that day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.97,0:38:04.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wished forit very strongly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.91,0:38:10.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.55,0:38:14.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.42,0:38:20.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's not here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.36,0:38:28.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That {\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.30,0:38:30.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe he overslept.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.08,0:38:54.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if you try to pretty\nyourself up with this,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.15,0:38:56.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you can't hide your\ntrue nature!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.99,0:38:58.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.43,0:39:02.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This rouge doesn't become\nyou at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.76,0:39:06.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demon blood is good enough\nforyou!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.17,0:39:09.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.94,0:39:14.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.98,0:39:19.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I neverwanted to become\na human!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.42,0:39:25.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks forthe Sacred {\i1}Jewel....{\i0}\NIt's mine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.02,0:39:31.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll have to make it suck more\nblood filled with hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.29,0:39:34.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll slaughterthe villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.56,0:39:38.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Curse you! Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.73,0:39:42.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you intended to trick me\nfrom the very start!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.50,0:39:45.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Were yourwords all lies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.31,0:39:48.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not saying this on a whim.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.31,0:39:50.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will become a human.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.31,0:39:52.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So you can become...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.65,0:39:53.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.51,0:39:57.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.62,0:40:01.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then, next {\i1}is....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.32,0:40:06.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that {\i1}half-demon....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.60,0:40:13.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.93,0:40:16.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's not here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.57,0:40:19.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you've come, half-demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.71,0:40:21.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.37,0:40:23.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What did you just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.31,0:40:25.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I said, "half-demon."
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.35,0:40:30.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can't those ugly dog ears\nhearwhat I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.18,0:40:33.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.29,0:40:38.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't let a half-demon like\nyou have the Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.29,0:40:40.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will destroy you right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.33,0:40:44.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Die, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.73,0:40:46.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Begone, half-demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.30,0:40:47.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.30,0:40:53.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now the Sacred Jewel will be\ntainted with hatred and bitterness.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.91,0:41:04.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn! You tricked me!\NYou just used me?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.75,0:41:06.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then tell me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.39,0:41:08.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I shall nevercall you\N"half-demon"again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.85,0:41:10.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's what you said...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.76,0:41:11.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.63,0:41:14.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.16,0:41:20.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.58,0:41:35.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Serves you right!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.25,0:41:39.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With this, I can become\na real demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.69,0:41:43.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't let anyone call me\na half-demon again!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.49,0:41:46.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.16,0:41:50.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I believed in you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.90,0:41:53.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I trusted you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.07,0:41:56.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I neverdoubted you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.44,0:42:00.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yet you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.47,0:42:01.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.56,0:42:19.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}K-Kikyo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.59,0:42:23.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You dared {\i1}to....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.53,0:42:29.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister! Sister Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.34,0:42:31.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Mistress Kikyo!\N- She's badly injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.20,0:42:32.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How did you get this?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.64,0:42:38.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Am I going to die like this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.58,0:42:41.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't say anything more.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.38,0:42:45.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess that's okay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.45,0:42:49.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo, even though it ended\nlike this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.06,0:42:52.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I still feel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.06,0:42:58.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Sacred {\i1}Jewel....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.50,0:42:59.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just because of someone like {\i1}him....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.63,0:43:02.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Listen well, Kaede.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.00,0:43:07.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take the Sacred Jewel and\nburn it with my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.64,0:43:11.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So that it will neverfall into\nthe hands of evil again!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.22,0:43:17.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.88,0:43:19.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.86,0:43:26.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will take the Sacred Jewel\nwith me to the netherworld.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.17,0:43:35.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It has been fifty years...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.23,0:43:38.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}that Inuyasha has been sealed\nto the Sacred Tree.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.51,0:43:42.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha looks exactly the\nsame as he did then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.61,0:43:47.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}At that time, my sisterknew\nthat she was going to die.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.65,0:43:50.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So why did she choose the\NArrow of Sealing to seal{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.45,0:43:52.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}ratherthan the Sacred Arrow\nto destroy?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.12,0:43:56.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why did she seal Inuyasha\non the Sacred Tree,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.49,0:44:00.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Tree of Ages said to be able to\ntranscend time?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.13,0:44:04.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And Inuyasha was filled with\nhatred towards my sister{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.36,0:44:06.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}who took back the\NSacred Jewel{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.73,0:44:08.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and sealed him to\nthe Sacred Tree...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.77,0:44:12.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But why did he have such\na peaceful expression on his face?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.74,0:44:17.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I understand nothing, afterall.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.34,0:44:22.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will the day come\nwhen I understand it all?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.49,0:44:32.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,15 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.79,0:44:37.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's born!\NMy firstgrandchild!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.80,0:44:39.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A beautiful girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.70,0:44:40.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's {\i1}okay....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.67,0:44:41.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.17,0:44:44.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yourname is Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.64,0:44:47.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ka-go-me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.77,0:44:50.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So nice to meet you, Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.41,0:44:56.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,15 Years Later
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.05,0:45:00.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, {\i1}yourfriend....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.55,0:45:05.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The notes for practice?\NI'll bring them today.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.92,0:45:07.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.39,0:45:09.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.24,0:47:08.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There are rumors\nof one Hijiri-sama
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.87,0:47:10.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,who can protect people\nagainst demon birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.68,0:47:12.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hakudoshi hears of this\nand takes action.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.88,0:47:16.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Humans who fearthe birds\nhave gathered to worship him.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.92,0:47:18.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,By now, Princess Abi and herbirds
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.05,0:47:21.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,have begun an assault on\nthis Hijiri-sama's village.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.32,0:47:24.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even Inuyasha's red Tetsusaiga\ncannot hurt Hakudoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.36,0:47:27.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just then, a barrier-breaking\NSacred Arrow comes flying...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.03,0:47:32.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"The Single Arrow of Chaos"
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.46,0:47:33.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That can't be!
